import React from 'react' import './DesktopNavigation.css' import {useHistory} from 'react-router-dom' import LogoType from '../../../shared/images/logotype.png' import RoutingPath from '../../../routes/RoutingPath' import useContext from 'react' export const DesktopNavigation = () => { const history = useHistory() return (
history.push(RoutingPath.homeView)}>Products history.push(RoutingPath.homeView)}>Brands history.push(RoutingPath.homeView)}>News history.push(RoutingPath.homeView)}>Guidelines history.push(RoutingPath.loginView)}>Login
) }
